				<p class="news_content_date">2014-07-18</p>
				<h2>2014女青思沙龍：翻轉崩世代，關鍵在「妳」</h2>
				<h4></h4>
                <div id="media_contents" class="w80 container">
	                					<hr>
	                <p>&nbsp;<span id="docs-internal-guid-e3324218-48d7-d3f7-d2aa-33889579452b">
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">『2014女青思沙龍：翻轉崩世代，關鍵在「妳」</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 184.2pt;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> －崩世代的女性青年就業』</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">身在紛亂時代的妳，站在十字路口上，</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">札札實實地感受到對於未來的被剝奪感嗎？</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">身為女青年的妳，遊蕩在崩世代與小確幸的交叉點，</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">這般看似平衡且平等的狀態，是一種集體的安慰，又或者背後是個大不幸？</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">我們需要加速思考的代謝，重新解構女性在就業、經濟、婚育上，如何突破重圍？ &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> &nbsp;邀您一起 女青 思沙龍。</span></p>
<br />
<ol style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">
    <li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">參加對象：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">全國女青年為主，16~40歲</span></p>
    </li>
    <li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">
    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">主講人：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">台灣職業安全健康連線 黃怡翎 執行長</span></p>
    </li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 90.1pt;text-indent: -90.1pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">三、活動時間：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">2014年7月29日（星期二），18：20 - 21：00</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 90.1pt;text-indent: -90.1pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">四、活動地點：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">慕哲咖啡(台北市中正區紹興北街3號)</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 83.1pt;text-indent: -77.1pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: 標楷體; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">*活動現場將備有點心與茶飲，邀您一同共享！</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 84.1pt;text-indent: -84.1pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">五、主辦單位：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">民進黨婦女部</span></p>
